channel.title: CVE Feed for FUJI ELECTRIC CO., LTD. -- FRENIC RHC Loader
channel.description: The latest CVEs for FUJI ELECTRIC CO., LTD. -- FRENIC RHC Loader

item.title: CVE-2023-29498|2024-08-02T14:07:46.378Z -- fuji%20electric%20co.%2C%20ltd. -- frenic%20rhc%20loader
item.description: Improper restriction of XML external entity reference (XXE) vulnerability exists in FRENIC RHC Loader v1.1.0.3 and earlier. If a user opens a specially crafted project file, sensitive information on the system where the affected product is installed may be disclosed.

item.title: CVE-2023-29167|2024-08-02T14:00:15.971Z -- fuji%20electric%20co.%2C%20ltd. -- frenic%20rhc%20loader
item.description: Out-of-bound reads vulnerability exists in FRENIC RHC Loader v1.1.0.3. If a user opens a specially crafted FNE file, sensitive information on the system where the affected product is installed may be disclosed or arbitrary code may be executed.

item.title: CVE-2023-29160|2024-08-02T14:00:15.704Z -- fuji%20electric%20co.%2C%20ltd. -- frenic%20rhc%20loader
item.description: Stack-based buffer overflow vulnerability exists in FRENIC RHC Loader v1.1.0.3. If a user opens a specially crafted FNE file, sensitive information on the system where the affected product is installed may be disclosed or arbitrary code may be executed.
